name: Jumpy Cat
overview: When most people look at Jumpy Cat, they would assume that the games is easy. WRONG! This game is possibly one of the hardest games on the Wii U™. With the calm music playing, and the quacking of the ducks, this game that you would assume to be easy, becomes even more difficult. Think you have what it takes to master Jumpy Cat? Jumpy Cat was removed from the Wii U eShop due to having stolen art assets.
